 Under a thunderstorm soaked sky an ancient portal awakens and in that instant beckoned us to the stars and beyond....

 A dazzling journey of the imagination. With influences from Vangelis and Jarre, Medwyn creates an inspired album that is majestic, dramatic, packed with new sounds and invention.

 Designed to play as one continuous piece the music weaves through variations on a theme
and a real-time rainstorm blends to create an amazing atmosphere.
